content:
## 世界

- id: {{ world.id }}
- 名称: {{ world.name }}
- 描述: {{ world.description }}
- language: {{ world.language }}

## 模拟

- id: {{ simulation.id }}
- 当前时间: {{ simulation.current_time }}

## 用户输入

{{ user_input }}

## 用户角色 id

{{ user_character_id }}

## 角色

{% for entry in actors %}
- id: {{ entry.character.id }}; 姓名: {{ entry.character.name }}; 描述: {{ entry.character.description }}; 公开状态: {{ entry.character.public_state }}; 当前活动: {{ entry.character.current_activity.name }}{% if entry.location %}; 地点: {{ entry.location.name }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 固定台词锚点

这些台词已经是最终内容，将由引擎插入。不要改写。

{% for anchor in speech_anchors %}
Speech {{ anchor.index }}:
- character id: {{ anchor.character_id }}
- character name: {{ anchor.character_name }}
- exact text: {{ anchor.text }}
- accepted action summary: {{ anchor.action_summary }}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 协调状态

- status: {{ coordination_result.status }}
- stopped reason: {{ coordination_result.stopped_reason }}

## 已接受行动

{% for entry in coordination_result.accepted_actions %}
Accepted action {{ loop.index0 }}:
- actor id: {{ entry.actor_id }}
- start offset seconds: {{ entry.start_offset_seconds }}
- end offset seconds: {{ entry.end_offset_seconds }}
- summary: {{ entry.summary }}
- action type: {{ entry.action.type }}
- label: {{ entry.action.label }}
- target ids: {{ entry.action.target_ids }}
- utterance: {{ entry.action.utterance }}
- expected effects: {{ entry.action.expected_effects }}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endfor %}

## 协调问题（如果有）

{% if coordination_result.problem %}
- type: {{ coordination_result.problem.type }}
- time offset seconds: {{ coordination_result.problem.time_offset_seconds }}
- involved actor ids: {{ coordination_result.problem.involved_actor_ids }}
- description: {{ coordination_result.problem.description }}
- needs user decision: {{ coordination_result.problem.needs_user_decision }}
{% else %}
- 无
{% endif %}

只返回 NarrationInsertionProposal JSON。
